    "description": "《Marauders》是一款设定在假想 1990 年代的第一人称多人战术射击游戏，第一次世界大战从未结束，地球工业化的程度到了崩溃边缘，许多人纷纷逃到外星球。玩家将扮演被称为“掠夺者”的太空雇佣兵，穿上一身装备并驾驶飞船穿梭于危机四伏的银河系，收集任何可以帮助自己生存的物品，并不择手段活下来。在每一场对战中，玩家可以放胆袭击庞大的护卫舰，获得大量战利品然后立即升级装备，并胆颤心惊地在移动的小行星上着陆。玩家还必须紧盯其他有着同样目标的敌人，用子弹阻止对方的探索行动。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><br><strong>逼真的柴油朋克世界：</strong>探索第一次世界大战仍持续进行的残酷反乌托邦世界，此时的人们只能借由搜刮和探索行星来求生<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/7ed4a95dc5f63db8e32976ca8c25e605.poster.avif?t=1760719452\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/7ed4a95dc5f63db8e32976ca8c25e605.webm?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/7ed4a95dc5f63db8e32976ca8c25e605.mp4?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>突袭、搜刮、逃脱：</strong>在科幻战场上展开掠夺行动，采取大胆的突袭动作来掠夺物品，然后活着离开以领取战利品，并转换为可观的利益<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/d78631278a4dcdd1c15ade69c63236f7.poster.avif?t=1760719452\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/d78631278a4dcdd1c15ade69c63236f7.webm?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/d78631278a4dcdd1c15ade69c63236f7.mp4?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>第一人称战术射击：</strong>当个独行侠或是与另外三名玩家合作，在逼真的子弹模拟体验中力抗敌方队伍和 AI 对手，从激烈的战斗生存下来<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/aa9793909eb89fc8ce2366af2923e06c.poster.avif?t=1760719452\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/aa9793909eb89fc8ce2366af2923e06c.webm?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/aa9793909eb89fc8ce2366af2923e06c.mp4?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>永久保留装备和经验值：</strong>在每一场对战中留下最佳装备，用模块调整您的惯用武器，同时使用经验值解锁新道具来提高生存几率<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/5bc6b37e3a0686b20f2c0bfad9b11929.poster.avif?t=1760719452\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/5bc6b37e3a0686b20f2c0bfad9b11929.webm?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/5bc6b37e3a0686b20f2c0bfad9b11929.mp4?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>可升级的太空船和震撼的科幻缠斗：</strong>升级自己的飞船武器、用收集到的资源打造全新飞船，或是强行夺走别人的飞船<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/cfbf138daf91393d6a5b111d3f4a3cf6.poster.avif?t=1760719452\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/cfbf138daf91393d6a5b111d3f4a3cf6.webm?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789480/extras/cfbf138daf91393d6a5b111d3f4a3cf6.mp4?t=1760719452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
